{"tid":2096162,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急求偵探］ 唔見咗iPhone 有啲Apple Watch 問題想問","createTime":"2020-07-06T03:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T04:05:48.000Z","uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7250ac7fef7c9d02a521f3b401fff02f2f3c354","tid":2096162,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"落完街返屋企過咗陣唔見電話 <br />\n唔肯定跌喺屋企定街<br />\n嗰frd唔比開alarm話嘈醒佢啊媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隻錶係無上網版<br />\n有幾個問題想問<br />\n1.喺屋企仲收到whatsapp 但過幾分鐘後收唔到（懷疑冇電）<br />\n2.開過相機 漆黑一片 開倒數會有閃光燈<br />\n3.個frd打比我 隻錶有反應 又係過幾分鐘收唔到<br />\n過完呢3件事過幾分鐘就有電話消失嘅icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪代表我部電話仲喺屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔見電話係咪要去狗屋報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b689809a0cab4f67b0804883b7ee18b69910f1d","tid":2096162,"uid":293943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"搵電腦 借電話開icloud find my iphone"},{"pid":"cfc23a526de3d59293f12d03fad5a30b158dce71","tid":2096162,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b689809a0cab4f67b0804883b7ee18b69910f1d","tid":2096162,"uid":293943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"搵電腦 借電話開icloud find my iphone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"試過 佢停留喺我落街個位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ca09140437d23122e29087b65c884edf63abfc","tid":2096162,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc23a526de3d59293f12d03fad5a30b158dce71","tid":2096162,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b689809a0cab4f67b0804883b7ee18b69910f1d","tid":2096162,"uid":293943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03